Wow! What a conversation. Did you listen in live?! 
This week Head of Admissions, Myisha Procter @thesequinunicorn encouraged us all to leave behind what no longer serves us and do only what lights your soul on fire.

Check out the replay and let us know your thoughts on this unforgettable conversation with the incredible @danifaig an IIN Alumni who recently completed the 6 mont accelerated Health Coach Training Program Course. A busy mom Dani is turning her passion for wellness into a fulfilling path as a health coach and she shares tips on how you can do it to!
